# Component Structure

Components should be organized in the following structure:

1. Create components in the `src/components` directory
2. Each component should have its own directory with the component name
3. Component files should use TypeScript (.tsx extension)
4. Use Tailwind CSS for styling
5. Use named exports for components

Example component structure:
```
src/components/
  ├── Hero/
  │   └── Hero.tsx
  ├── Navbar/
  │   └── Navbar.tsx
  ├── Projects/
  │   └── Projects.tsx
  ├── Skills/
  │   └── Skills.tsx
  └── Contact/
      └── Contact.tsx
```
